📚 Key Takeaways

✔ CSV stores tabular data as plain text
✔ `csv.reader()` reads CSV files
✔ `csv.writer()` writes CSV files
✔ `openpyxl` manages Excel files
✔ Workbooks contain worksheets
✔ `append()` adds rows easily
✔ CSV is faster, while Excel supports advanced features

